snippet.title: Full Moon Event | Shop Titans
snippet.description:
Design and build a thriving shop in this tycoon simulation adventure! Outfit your heroes and champions with epic gear, and send them on quests to defeat powerful bosses! https://playshoptitans.com/  

From distant lands come the dragons of legend! Armed with a wealth of knowledge, they are willing to share these exotic crafting methods to those that would befriend them. Turn Legendary items into Flawless during every Full Moon. 

Full Moon 6.0 Release Notes: 
https://playshoptitans.com/news/version-6-0-0-release-notes/

#ShopTitans #Kabam
